{"data":{"prismicProject":{"uid":"samsungseriftv","first_publication_date":"2017-12-29T16:27:55+0000","last_publication_date":"2018-09-19T21:19:22+0000","data":{"project_title":{"text":"Samsung Serif TV"},"project_role":{"text":"Lead Frontend Developer"},"project_tech_stack":{"text":"HTML(5), CSS(3), SASS, JavaScript & jQuery, Grunt, threesixty.js, lazyload.js"},"project_type":null,"project_visit_website_link":{"url":"http://www.seriftv.com/"},"project_main_text":{"text":"This is a static website for the brand new Samsung product, the Serif TV. The product was designed by the acclaimed design duo, Ronan and Erwan Bouroullec, and aims to “blur the lines between furniture and technology”. The website was designed and built to reflect the soft, subtle and elegant aesthetic of the product itself – taking elements such as ‘curtain’ mode from the product and translating that within the site. The pages of the site let the user explore the ‘design’, ‘craft’ and ‘lifestyle’ of the Serif TV, as well as the product range and a store locator."},"project_imac":{"localFile":{"childImageSharp":{"sizes":{"tracedSVG":"data:image/svg+xml,%3csvg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' width='400' height='317' viewBox='0 0 400 317' version='1'%3e%3cpath d='M49 43c-3 3-3 179 0 182 2 2 3 2 61 2h59l1 3 2 3h58l1-3v-3h119l2-3c3-4 3-176 0-180l-2-3H200C52 41 51 41 49 43m10 11l1 123v36h282V54H59m147 23l3 4v103h-12c-8 0-12 0-14-2l-4-1 12 6 13 6h12c9 0 12-1 13-2s0-2-2-3l-3-1V80l3-2 4-2h-14c-13 0-14 0-11 1m-17 4l-3 1-2 1c-1 1-2 2-3 1-2 0-2 0-1 1 2 1 2 1 0 1-1 1-2 0-2-1h-1l-1 2c-3 0-3 5-3 44v42l3 2c3 0 4 2 4 3l1 3v-3c0-3 4-2 5 2 1 2 6 2 8 1h2c0 2 2 1 1-1 0-2-4-3-4-1h-2l-3-2v-1c1-1 1-1-2-2l-3-1-1-41V91l4-2 5-1h1l-1-2v-2c2-1 3-4 1-4l-3 1m-19 176c-2 0-3 1-3 2 0 2 1 2 33 2l33-1v-3h-63' fill='%23021212' fill-rule='evenodd'/%3e%3c/svg%3e","aspectRatio":1.2618296529968454,"src":"/static/a24651c078436e79abbfc08bb7e1b567-3bf068be7db345892135c80a4c29ebf6-3cc0b.png","srcSet":"/static/a24651c078436e79abbfc08bb7e1b